00:00:56.080 --> 00:00:57.520
Twelve years ago,

00:00:57.720 --> 00:00:58.960
you killed my family,

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:00.400
disfigured my face,

00:01:00.560 --> 00:01:02.360
falsely claimed to be my savior,

00:01:02.520 --> 00:01:03.600
blinded my eyes,

00:01:03.800 --> 00:01:05.360
and deceived me from the truth.

00:01:06.480 --> 00:01:07.840
For twelve years,

00:01:07.920 --> 00:01:09.640
you seized my family's wealth,

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:11.360
humiliated and abused me,

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.720
and famed me for opium trafficking,

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:15.080
making me die unjustly.

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:16.800
Twelve years later,

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:18.960
all sins will be repaid.

00:01:20.240 --> 00:01:21.040
I

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:22.120
have returned.

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:31.520
[Episode 1]

00:01:32.820 --> 00:01:36.560
[One month ago]

00:01:42.520 --> 00:01:44.480
[Blycher Hotel]

00:01:45.100 --> 00:01:45.860
Move along now.

00:01:45.860 --> 00:01:46.660
Go play over there.

00:01:50.980 --> 00:01:51.660
Mr. Sun,

00:01:51.980 --> 00:01:53.180
this batch of opium

00:01:53.340 --> 00:01:55.380
will surely transport you to bliss.

00:02:22.700 --> 00:02:24.340
Miss Wang, your legs are so fair,

00:02:24.780 --> 00:02:27.140
though somewhat cold.

00:02:29.050 --> 00:02:30.780
[Mr. Sun]

00:02:30.780 --> 00:02:31.820
How dare you!

00:02:33.100 --> 00:02:35.060
[Wang Wan'er, daughter of Wang Penghui]
Wenbin will return home soon.

00:02:35.580 --> 00:02:37.260
We are already engaged.

00:02:38.060 --> 00:02:39.460
You'd better behave.

00:02:39.860 --> 00:02:41.140
Keep your distance from me.

00:02:48.060 --> 00:02:50.260
Have you arranged the shipment?

00:02:50.540 --> 00:02:51.540
All arranged.

00:02:52.060 --> 00:02:54.300
Time and place are set.

00:02:54.580 --> 00:02:55.420
Rest assured.

00:02:56.340 --> 00:02:58.300
Is the transaction data secured?

00:02:58.580 --> 00:03:00.060
All locked in the safe.

00:03:20.460 --> 00:03:23.100
Finally found proof of their opium deal.

00:03:24.020 --> 00:03:26.660
The Marshal of Song City is after opium?

00:03:26.860 --> 00:03:28.460
Then I shall lure him in.

00:03:44.500 --> 00:03:44.980
Someone is here.

00:03:45.140 --> 00:03:45.820
Go take a look.

00:03:55.060 --> 00:03:55.860
Who is it?

00:04:39.880 --> 00:04:44.720
[Chen Wenbin, Marshal]

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:34.600
[Liu Rumeng]

00:05:50.180 --> 00:05:51.900
Boss, it was stolen!

00:05:52.260 --> 00:05:53.060
- What?
- What?

00:05:53.380 --> 00:05:54.500
Seal the hotel now!

00:06:09.340 --> 00:06:10.500
The place is full of guards.

00:06:10.540 --> 00:06:11.620
You cannot escape.

00:06:11.660 --> 00:06:12.460
Work with me.

00:06:33.340 --> 00:06:35.060
Who are you?

00:06:48.700 --> 00:06:49.860
You exposed me,

00:06:49.980 --> 00:06:51.660
then you save me?

00:06:52.180 --> 00:06:53.060
Why?

00:07:00.940 --> 00:07:01.740
For you.

00:07:04.820 --> 00:07:06.820
Marshal Chen is back in Song City!

00:07:15.340 --> 00:07:16.420
Wenbin,

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:21.660
is this flower for me?

00:07:21.660 --> 00:07:23.420
Boss, this is the man.

00:07:24.300 --> 00:07:26.100
Why did you return without telling me?

00:07:27.060 --> 00:07:28.460
Sorry, sir.

00:07:29.500 --> 00:07:31.420
Something important was stolen.

00:07:32.300 --> 00:07:33.740
To catch the thief,

00:07:34.180 --> 00:07:35.100
please

00:07:35.340 --> 00:07:36.420
work with us.

00:07:37.860 --> 00:07:40.380
Shut up! Do you know who he is?

00:07:40.700 --> 00:07:43.340
He is the son
of Song City Military Governor.

00:07:43.340 --> 00:07:44.980
Chen Wenbin, Marshal Chen!

00:07:46.200 --> 00:07:47.320
[Invitation]

00:07:50.180 --> 00:07:52.460
And he is my fiancé.

00:07:53.020 --> 00:07:54.380
I was blind.

00:07:54.820 --> 00:07:55.420
My apologies,

00:07:55.940 --> 00:07:57.020
Marshal Chen,

00:07:57.620 --> 00:07:58.540
Miss Wang.

00:08:03.080 --> 00:08:08.320
[Memory of
Lin Qingyi, Lin Wenruo, and Lin Zongyao]

00:08:17.060 --> 00:08:18.460
Do you want to know

00:08:18.900 --> 00:08:21.260
