00:08:21.980 --> 00:08:22.860
It was my father.

00:08:23.260 --> 00:08:24.380
Your so-called savior.

00:08:25.100 --> 00:08:26.340
He planned it.

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:29.720
[Lin Wenruo, father of Lin Qingyi]

00:08:31.820 --> 00:08:32.620
Qingmao,

00:08:33.060 --> 00:08:34.180
my father said

00:08:34.660 --> 00:08:36.100
as the Wang family's executioner,

00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:38.020
your life is a threat.

00:08:39.500 --> 00:08:42.740
Today you must die.

00:08:57.980 --> 00:08:59.860
After the Lin family fire,

00:08:59.860 --> 00:09:01.660
my father saved you.

00:09:01.860 --> 00:09:04.540
He let you live ten more years
as Qingmao.

00:09:04.780 --> 00:09:05.540
You know,

00:09:05.540 --> 00:09:06.180
in these ten years,

00:09:06.180 --> 00:09:08.700
seeing your ugly face

00:09:08.700 --> 00:09:09.980
in front of me

00:09:10.500 --> 00:09:11.980
made me sick?

00:09:31.380 --> 00:09:34.100
[Hua]

00:09:34.100 --> 00:09:34.700
Meng,

00:09:35.300 --> 00:09:36.260
